    <main class="container-md">
        <div>
            <h1>A general purpose bot, for your general needs.</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="padding-top: 30px;">
            <h3>Trixy will take care of most of your basic needs in the server, be it moderating, leveling up
                members or just playing music.<br>
                All with just a single command. Quick. Simple.</h3>
        </div>
    </main>

    <div class="line-breaker"><img src="/media/line-breaker1.png" alt="Decorative line breaker." /></div>

    <article class="container-sm">
        <div class="col">
            <section class="col" id="left">
                <div>
                    <h4>Basic moderation and member management</h4>
                    <p>Add roles, mute annoying people, ban missbehaving members or just purge some messages in the
                        channel.</p>
                </div>
                <span>
                    <img src="media/cmd-proof/mute-cmd.png" alt="Muting a member." />
                </span>
            </section>

            <section class="col" id="right">
                <div>
                    <h4>Random images and facts</h4>
                    <p>A collection of commands that serve content. A random cat image? NASA's daily space photo? All
                        yours.</p>
                </div>
                <span>
                    <img src="media/cmd-proof/cat-cmd.png" alt="Asking for a cat iamge." />
                </span>
            </section>

            <section class="col" id="left">
                <div>
                    <h4>Utility commands</h4>
                    <p>Get information about users or guilds, set a reminder or lookup the weather somewhere.</p>
                </div>
                <span>
                    <img src="media/cmd-proof/weather-cmd.png" alt="Looking up the weather." />
                </span>
            </section>

            <section class="col" id="right">
                <div>
                    <h4>Play music from YouTube</h4>
                    <p>Play, skip, pause and resume songs, list the queue and see what song is playing.</p>
                </div>
                <span>
                    <img src="media/cmd-proof/play-cmd.png" alt="Playing a song." />
                </span>
            </section>

            <section class="col" id="left">
                <div>
                    <h4>Level system</h4>
                    <p>Grind experience and climb the leaderboard for additional rewards. (Role rewards to be added
                        soon.)</p>
                </div>
                <span>
                    <img src="media/cmd-proof/level-cmd.png" alt="Checking level progression." />
                </span>
            </section>
        </div>
    </article>

    <div class="container-fluid line-breaker"><img src="/media/line-breaker2.png" alt="Decorative line breaker." /></div>

    <section>
        <div class="container">
            <h4>Dashboard (To Be Added)</h4>
            <p>A description will go here eventually.</p>
        </div>
        <span>
            <img src="media/placeholder-dark.jpg" alt="Screenshot of the Dashboard. TBA!" />
        </span>
    </section>

    <footer class="container-fluid">
        <div id="foot1">
            <span id="footer-logo"><img src="/media/trixy.png" alt="Trixy" width="70" height="70"
                    style="border-radius: 50%; margin: 10px;"><h1>TRIXY</h1></span>
            <span id="contact-us">CONTACT US</span>
            <span id="contacts">
                <a href="https://discord.gg/ZbUQ8Mh"><img src="/media/discord.png" alt="Discord" height="40px"></a>
                <a href="mailto://merilaxreloaded@gmail.com"><img src="/media/mail.png" alt="Email" height="40px"></a>
            </span>
        </div>
